helpText:
Private commands: ** !evetime | !stat | !about | !char | !corp | !jita | !amarr | !dodixie | !rens | !pc**
Enter !help COMMAND in the bot private message for additional info
helpAuth: *auth* command helps to authenticate you by EVE Online character. Send *!auth* command to the bot for additional details.
helpTime: *evetime* command displays current EVE Online time
helpStat:
*stat* command display alliance stats by time interval
Examples: !stat m | !stat d | !stat 2018 | !stat 2018/03
helpAbout: *about* command displays information about the bot
helpChar:
*char* command displays information about in game character by name
Example: *!char Don Chack*
helpCorp:
*corp* command displays information about corporation by name
Example: *!corp Nebula Alba*
helpJita:
this command displays information about the item price in a specified trade hub
Example: *!jita Robotics*
helpPc:
this command displays information about the global item price
Example: *!pc Robotics*
commandToPrivate: This command should be sent as a private message to the bot!
